e work and focus on other things."), mdx("p", null, "Studies () about the incapacity of people with OCD (obsessive compulsive disorder) of feeling that satisfaction after a job well done (cleaning hands, closing doors, etc) show a relation between serotonin levels and that feeling of satisfaction. Serotonin makes people satisfied and less anxious. There are also direct links between serotonin levels and reduced anxiety. In fact, SSRIs (selective serotonin receptors inhibitors) are prescribed to reduce anxiety for people with ", mdx("a", _extends({
